scene.message:
Night Queen: Hmhmhm...{nl}
To think you'd chase me{nl}
this far...{waitkey}{clearbox}You should have just waited{nl}
quietly for the{nl}
"Eternal Night."{waitkey}{clearbox}Very well, as you wish,{nl}
I'll grant you despair.{waitkey}{clearbox}I won't go down as easily{nl}
as Tomomi did.{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Hmhmhm...{waitkey}{ret}

Masked Girl: Why do you{nl}
try to protect the school?{waitkey}{clearbox}A school like this...{wait_fr:30} a school{nl}
like this should just{nl}
disappear!{waitkey}{ret}

Masked Boy: Night Queen,{nl}
we shall lend you our power.{waitkey}{clearbox}That said, this place is{nl}
a bit cramped to combine{nl}
the strength of three.{waitkey}{clearbox}We'll invite you to the{nl}
top floor.{wait_fr:30} Follow us{nl}
at your leisure.{waitkey}{ret}

Ready to head to the floor{nl}
above?{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Masked Boy: Then keep{nl}
honing yourselves.{waitkey}{clearbox}Whichever side wins,{nl}
it makes no difference to me.{waitkey}{ret}
